originalText.text: Had them replace some back doors on a retail building, in NY. They were super affordable and really quick at for a commercial metal door manufacturer. The new doors shut properly now so that the locking system works properly on the units that were having issues. So, I'd say that both myself and my business tenants are very pleased with the quality of their metal exterior doors as well as their speedy service.
